---
title: Lemon-Pepper Chicken Thighs and Mushrooms with Spinach Caesar Salad
description: Lemon-pepper and Parmesan impart this hearty chicken and mushroom bake with classic Caesar salad flavours. It's simple, convenient and delicious. What more could you ask for?
